text: Claude Feidt (7 March 1936 - 13 October 2020) was a French Roman Catholic prelate. He was born in Audun-le-Roman, France. He was Archbishop of Chambéry from 1985 to 1999 and of Aix from 1999 to 2010. Feidt died on 13 October 2020 at a hospital in Le Puy-en-Velay, France at the age of 84.Archbishop Claude Feidt ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2020 deaths Category:French Roman Catholic archbishops Category:People from Chambéry
